data.description: Welcome to 206 E Center Street, Gifford, IL! This beautiful ranch-style home located on a dead-end road boasts 3 bedrooms and 1.5 baths, providing the perfect blend of comfort and style. Step inside and discover a haven of updates and tasteful renovations. The living spaces feature hardwood floors (installed in 2018) that seamlessly flow from room to room, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. The kitchen, a focal point of this home, underwent a complete transformation in 2018. Revel in the delight of a renovated kitchen with new counters, cabinets, backsplash, and a modern sink - a culinary enthusiast's dream. Other updates in the kitchen include Microwave (2018) and dishwasher (2023).  All 3 bedrooms have been adorned with new carpet, new doors, and new closet doors in 2018. The entire house has been treated to a fresh coat of paint, creating a clean canvas for you to infuse your personal style. Cozy up by the unique live-edge fireplace hearth and mantle, a distinctive feature that adds character and warmth to the living room. The gas log fireplace insert, installed in 2018, ensures both comfort and efficiency during colder months. In 2021, the half bath underwent a stylish renovation, offering a modern and convenient space for both residents and guests. The attention to detail continues into the heated two-car garage, recently redone with drywall, providing a functional and aesthetically pleasing space for your vehicles and hobbies. Step outside into the expansive backyard and discover your own private oasis. A raised garden bed awaits your green thumb, while a garden shed provides convenient storage for tools and outdoor essentials. Enjoy al fresco dining or simply unwind on the back patio, taking in the beauty of the surroundings. This property at 206 E Center Street is not just a house; it's a meticulously updated and thoughtfully designed home that invites you to live in comfort and style. Don't miss the opportunity to make it yours - schedule a viewing today and experience the charm of Gifford living at its finest!
